responseText: NSLOCTEXT("[70199B914E7E03A9706A1499CF20B1FD]", "7E3B589B4963AA73B23CE29B87E6588D", "Our war priests have divulged the evil intent of our enemy. The goblins have taken our fallen and resurrected them as undead minions. The remains of our swordmen must be reclaimed then burned in the outpost pyre. This is the only way we can ensure that our fallen are honored and kept safe from the dark arts of the enemy.")
